!恆星的<br />數目<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nso.edu/PR/answerbook/magnitude.html |title=星等 |publisher=National Solar Observatory—Sacramento Peak |accessdate=2006-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080206074842/http://www.nso.edu/PR/answerbook/magnitude.html |archivedate=2008-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
